findings.title: Owner can change feeCollector address
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the feeCollector address, which could lead to unauthorized changes.

findings.title: Owner can enable/disable acceptOnlyLp
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to enable or disable the acceptOnlyLp feature.

findings.title: Owner can change migrator contract
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the migrator contract.

findings.title: Owner can change fees
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify fees, which could lead to potential security risks.

findings.title: Owner can add addresses in fee discount list
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to add addresses in the fee discount list without any restrictions.
